### Listar assinaturas
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/assinaturas/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Criar assinatura
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/assinaturas/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Netflix",
  "descricao": "Streaming de vídeos",
  "valor": 29.90,
  "periodicidade": "mensal",
  "data_inicio": "2025-01-01",
  "categoria": 1,
  "ativa": true
}

### Buscar assinatura por ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/assinaturas/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Atualizar assinatura
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/v1/assinaturas/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Netflix Premium",
  "descricao": "Streaming de vídeos - Plano Premium",
  "valor": 39.90,
  "periodicidade": "mensal",
  "data_inicio": "2025-01-01",
  "categoria": 1,
  "ativa": true
}

### Cancelar assinatura
PATCH http://localhost:8000/api/v1/assinaturas/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ativa": false,
  "data_cancelamento": "2025-01-20"
}

### Deletar assinatura
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/v1/assinaturas/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}